  <title>Gio.FileMonitorFlags</title>
  <p>Flags used to set what a <link xref="Gio.FileMonitor"/> will watch for.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>FileMonitorFlags.NONE</code></title>
  <p>No flags set.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>FileMonitorFlags.WATCH_MOUNTS</code></title>
  <p>Watch for mount events.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>FileMonitorFlags.SEND_MOVED</code></title>
  <p>Pair DELETED and CREATED events caused
  by file renames (moves) and send a single G_FILE_MONITOR_EVENT_MOVED
  event instead (NB: not supported on all backends; the default
  behaviour -without specifying this flag- is to send single DELETED
  and CREATED events).</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>FileMonitorFlags.WATCH_HARD_LINKS</code></title>
  <p>Watch for changes to the file made
  via another hard link. Since 2.36.</p>
</item>
